## ğŸ“Œ Overview & Objectives

Uncle JJ is a soulful, AI-powered digital mentor who offers drop-in voice and text conversations to curious, growth-minded individuals. Designed for those seeking motivation, clarity, or a dose of real talk, Uncle JJ delivers emotionally resonant insights using a mix of pre-written wisdom snippets and AI-generated elaboration. His tone is relaxed, cinematic, and groundedâ€”think porch talk at golden hour.

This project is a creative experiment and personal tool for a values-aligned community. It prioritizes vibe, character, and emotional depth over traditional productivity metrics.

